short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Uploads Data from MyCareTeam Meter Upload application

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The MyCareTeam meter upload extension is used to upload your meter readings to the MyCareTeam web site (www.mycareteam.com).  To use this extension, you must also download the MyCareTeam meter control from the web site after you have logged into your account.
